product_desc:
Once again the name of this Great Firm is AMCOR HOLDINGS LTD..

As one of world’s leading packaging manufacturers, Amcor offers customers the highest quality in innovative and sustainable packaging solutions, and partnerships built on service, reliability and excellence. Our extensive global footprint puts us on our customer’s doorstep wherever they do business so big or small, Amcor can provide leading packaging solutions for any organisation.

Amcor offers a broad range of packaging related products and services, including packaging for beverages, food, healthcare, personal and homecare, tobacco, and industrial applications.
name: AMCOR HOLDINGS
